10d3216a-a59e-44b6-8b06-80917f94a939.title: Dark Mage
10d3216a-a59e-44b6-8b06-80917f94a939.text: Quiet! You must not break my concentration!

8841d1dc-bc3f-4c6f-93dd-fb464575716a.title: Dark Mage
8841d1dc-bc3f-4c6f-93dd-fb464575716a.text:
Well, if my concentration is broken while keeping
this gate open, then, if we are lucky, everyone within
a one mile radius will either have their heads explode,
or will be consumed internally by the creatures of the Abyss.

3bf1b58d-c0ef-4239-ad83-e74a47e0829b.title: <player>
3bf1b58d-c0ef-4239-ad83-e74a47e0829b.text: Erm... And if we are unlucky?

42805581-d5ae-41a0-85a1-fb59d512d44d.title: Dark Mage
42805581-d5ae-41a0-85a1-fb59d512d44d.text:
If we are unlucky, then the entire universe will begin to
fold in upon itself, and all reality as we know it will be
annihilated in a single stroke.

6e28bef5-d96d-43cc-a378-1a79e482a978.title: Dark Mage
6e28bef5-d96d-43cc-a378-1a79e482a978.text:
Do you mean what am I doing here in Abyssal space,
or are you asking me what I consider my ultimate role,
to be in this voyage that we call life?

981e30e8-afb6-49fc-98ee-4a93813dbf8e.title: Dark Mage
981e30e8-afb6-49fc-98ee-4a93813dbf8e.text:
By remaining here and holding this portal open, I am
providing a permanent link between normal space and
this strange dimension that we call Abyssal space.

3515c9d4-7391-4bd0-bb32-afbeef798d95.title: Dark Mage
3515c9d4-7391-4bd0-bb32-afbeef798d95.text:
As long as this spell remains in effect, we have the
capability to teleport into abyssal space at will.

ecff3c9c-f06b-4f82-9e21-f0262c949a61.title: Dark Mage
ecff3c9c-f06b-4f82-9e21-f0262c949a61.text: Now leave me be! I can afford no distraction in my task!

b218e63b-9a40-4ee3-b14f-d7a080c20049.title: Dark Mage
b218e63b-9a40-4ee3-b14f-d7a080c20049.text:
Good. I'm attempting to subdue the elemental
mechanisms of the universe to my will. Inane chatter
from random idiots is not helping me achieve this!

627f556e-e3d9-4c49-b198-429e2e480635.title: Dark Mage
627f556e-e3d9-4c49-b198-429e2e480635.text: What? Oh... Very well. What did you want?

328e27ce-751b-4a93-b1c0-cf2e4f06abea.title: Dark Mage
328e27ce-751b-4a93-b1c0-cf2e4f06abea.text:
Fine. A simple transfiguration spell should resolve things
for you.

41bc0d65-8d32-4fc2-bc78-069c8b179336.title: <player>
41bc0d65-8d32-4fc2-bc78-069c8b179336.text: Actually, I can't think of anything right now...

ae40ad66-6518-4b9f-a45e-b54011a37e7a.title: Dark Mage
ae40ad66-6518-4b9f-a45e-b54011a37e7a.text:
Honestly, you have no idea of the pressure I am under
attempting to keep this portal open!

options.text: I need your help with something...

f531c233-8d72-4bea-b613-b53476233b87.title: <player>
f531c233-8d72-4bea-b613-b53476233b87.text: I need your help with something.

options.text: Can I have a new essence pouch?
Actually, I don't need anything right now.

1ed5418b-1ff5-46f1-9b46-03193aa8b5a5.title: <player>
1ed5418b-1ff5-46f1-9b46-03193aa8b5a5.text: Can I have a new essence pouch?

e184d50d-e2bd-41ed-a638-f9358f48d71d.title: Dark Mage
e184d50d-e2bd-41ed-a638-f9358f48d71d.text: Here. Be more careful with your belongings in future.

4f514331-f91b-41e9-8ca5-00a996617a19.text: You have been given a pouch.

d879884f-3b49-4984-aab6-097461e97aaa.title: Dark Mage
d879884f-3b49-4984-aab6-097461e97aaa.text:
Now can you leave me alone? I can't keep affording
these distractions!

8b632524-3f7e-4719-bbfa-d38e30601f89.title: Dark Mage
8b632524-3f7e-4719-bbfa-d38e30601f89.text:
You don't seem to have any pouches in need of repair.
Leave me alone!

b7233831-fbff-46e7-aafa-ebba760165d4.title: Dark Mage
b7233831-fbff-46e7-aafa-ebba760165d4.text:
There, I have repaired your pouches. Now leave me
alone. I'm concentrating!
